videos.description: Trae Young comes off the screen and throws it up to Clint Capela for the one-handed flush.

videos.headline: Young throws pinpoint lob to Capela for jam

videos.description: Trae Young finds himself pinned on the baseline and gets out of it by throwing the behind-the-back pass to Tony Snell for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Young gets fancy, goes behind-the-back to Snell for 3) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young gets fancy, goes behind-the-back to Snell for 3

videos.description: Russell Westbrook spins off Tony Snell and finishes the layup in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook leaves Snell in the dust with spin move) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook leaves Snell in the dust with spin move

videos.description: Russell Westbrook drains the 3-pointer right before the halftime buzzer giving him 25 points on the night.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook caps off 25-point half with a 3) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook caps off 25-point half with a 3

videos.description: Trae Young dribbles around multiple Wizards then throws it up to Clint Capela for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Young dribbles through Wizards, finds Capela for jam) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young dribbles through Wizards, finds Capela for jam

videos.description: Daniel Gafford knocks the lob away, then hustles down court for the two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gafford does it all for Wizards) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gafford does it all for Wizards

videos.description: Daniel Gafford shows out early in the fourth quarter with two emphatic dunks in the paint.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gafford continues stellar 2nd half with two huge 4th quarter dunks) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gafford continues stellar 2nd half with two huge 4th quarter dunks

videos.description: Trae Young has Raul Neto dancing as he gets the floater to fall.

videos.headline: Young dances on Neto, puts in floater

videos.description: John Collins nails the corner 3-pointer, then the Hawks get back-to-back stops to complete the comeback win over Wizards.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Collins' 3, Hawks' clutch defense secure win) 2021/05/12 ESHEET
